## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b12c5-173">L'exemple suivant montre comment définir la valeur de la propriété jointe <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b12c5-173">The following example shows how to set the value of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Serialization.WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty> dependency property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
CodeActivity code1 = new CodeActivity();  
Hashtable eventsHashtable = new Hashtable();  
eventsHashtable.Add("ExecuteCode", "methodName1");  
code1.SetValue(WorkflowMarkupSerializer.EventsProperty, eventsHashtable);  
```
